<div class="container">
  <p class="lead">What is PlanSource?</p>
  <p>PlanSource is a web and mobile application that allows you to upload plans that can be viewed on your mobile device.</p>
  <hr>
  <p class="lead">Who should use PlanSource?</p>
  <p>PlanSource is primarily people in the construction industry such as engineers, designers, contractors, etc, but can be used by anyone.</p>
  <hr>
  <p class="lead">What is a Viewer account?</p>
  <p>A Viewer account lets you view jobs and plans that have been shared with you.  Viewers also have the ability to print and reshare if the owner of the job allows it.<p>
  <hr>
  <p class="lead">Who should use a Viewer account?</p>
  <p>A Viewer account should be used by someone that doesn't need to upload or create jobs.  Viewers are shared jobs that the managers own and maintain. Generally these are contractors and people that are not project managers.</p>
  <hr>
  <p class="lead">What is a Manager account?</p>
  <p>A Manager account can do everything a viewer can plus create, edit, destroy, and share jobs and plans.  A Manager also has the ability to determine the plans that can be printed.</p>
  <hr>
  <p class="lead">Who should use a Manager account?</p>
  <p>A Manager should be used by someone that needs to create jobs or upload plans.  Managers usually have many Viewers that they share jobs with.  Generally these are project managers.</p>
  <hr>
  <p class="lead">Does it cost to create an account?</p>
  <p>Right now, all accounts are free, but in the future, Manager account will have a subscription required.<p>
  <hr>
  <p class="lead">How many jobs can I create?</p>
  <p>There isn't a limit to how many plans you can upload.</p>
  <hr>
  <p class="lead">How many plans can I upload?</p>
  <p>As many as you want!  There isn't a limit to how many plans you can upload.<p>
  <hr>
  <p class="lead">Can I share my jobs?</p>
  <p>Yes, all you need is the users email you wish to share with.  If the user doesn't have an account then they will receive an email.</p>
  <hr>
  <p class="lead">Can anyone reshare jobs I've shared with them?</p>
  <p>No, only people you allow to can reshare your jobs.<p>
  <hr>
  <p class="lead">How do I view my plans?</p>
  <p>You can download the plans in the browser, or install the one of the mobile applications on your device.<p>
  <hr>
  <p class="lead">Which mobile platforms are supported?</p>
  <p>Android and iPhone.</p>
  <hr>
  <p class="lead">Is the app free?</p>
  <p>The app is completely free.</p>
  <hr>
  <p class="lead">Can I print my plans?</p>
  <p>There are plans to implement printing, but as of right now printing is not available.</p>
